data.description: One-level home in a quiet Milwaukie neighborhood close to everything! Walk 1/2 a block to Ball-Michel Park, within minutes to all the schools, shopping, restaurants and more that the Milwaukie and Clackamas areas offer. Great living space with an open kitchen overlooking the living room. Fenced yard with patio and tool shed, a blank slate just waiting for all of your personal touches. Move-in ready, definitely a must see! [Home Energy Score = 3. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10220848]
